</div>
<div class="video-examples-featured">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="40u464" data-video-descrip="Kuwabara may act the tough guy, but Yusuke easily knocks him down to the curb without a sweat. And it turns out Kuwabara has been beaten by Yusuke 156 times by this point. But you gotta give the guy props for not giving up." data-video-title="Kuwabara" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/40u464_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/kuwabara_bruised_7.png" data-video-trope="Main/BoisterousWeakling" data-video-tropename="Boisterous Weakling" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="5.00" data-video-rating-count="4" data-video-media-sources="Manga/YuYuHakusho" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link featured-widget-vid">
<div class="featured-widget-vid-iframe">
<video id='featured-video-player' class='video-js vjs-default-skin vjs-16-9' controls data-setup='{"ga": {"eventsToTrack": ["error"]}}'>
</video>
</div>
</a>
<h2 class="bold font-l">Kuwabara</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Kuwabara may act the tough guy, but Yusuke easily knocks him down to the curb without a sweat. And it turns out Kuwabara has been beaten by Yusuke 156 times by this point. But you gotta give the guy props for not giving up. </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
